name: FFrameMetrics
doc: Metrics that correspond to a particular frame

TotalElapsedTime: The total amount of time, in seconds, since the capture started
FrameDelta: The total amount of time, in seconds, that this specific frame took to render (not accounting for dropped frames)
FrameNumber: The index of this frame from the start of the capture, including dropped frames
NumDroppedFrames: The number of frames we dropped in-between this frame, and the last one we captured
